<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 Not Found | Amora Hub</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 10rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            color: #E94057;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .error-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        .error-message {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8A2387, #E94057);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        .home-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
        <h2 class="error-title">Page Not Found</h2>
        <p class="error-message">
            Oops! It seems the page you're looking for has gone on a date and never came back.
            Let's get you back to finding your own perfect match.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="home-button">Back to Homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>